            </p>
            <div class="note_exaction">
                <b>La photo&nbsp;:</b> la forge, ca donne soif&nbsp;!!!
            </div>
            <div class="photo_exactions">
                <a href="http://www.compagniefranchedukhatovar.fr/piwigo/index.php?/category/36" rel="external"><img src="{{ asset('bundles/khatovarweb/images/camera.png') }}" class="photolink" alt="" />
